    <chapter num="2">
        <verse num="1">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Me mma nkumaa, meretwer&#603; yeinom mabr&#603; mo, na moany&#603; b&#596;ne. Na s&#603; obi y&#603; b&#596;ne a, y&#603;w&#596; &#596;kamafo&#596; bi, Agya no nky&#603;n, &#596;no ne &#390;teneneeni Yesu Kristo. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="2">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Na &#596;no ne y&#603;n b&#596;ne ho mpata, na &#603;ny&#603; y&#603;n de&#603; ho nko, na mmom wiase nyinaa de&#603; ho bi.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="3">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na s&#603; y&#603;di n’ahy&#603;de&#603; so a, &#603;no ara na y&#603;de hunu s&#603; y&#603;nim no. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="4">
            <block_quote>
                <content>De&#603; &#596;ka s&#603;: Menim no, na &#596;nni n’ahy&#603;de&#603; so&#596; no, y&#603; &#596;torofo&#596;, na nokor&#603; no nni ne mu. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="5">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Na obiara a &#596;di n’as&#603;m so&#596; no, ampa ara, &#596;no mu na Nyankop&#596;n d&#596; no awie p&#603;y&#603;. Yei na y&#603;de hunu s&#603; y&#603;w&#596; ne mu. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="6">
            <block_quote>
                <content> De&#603; &#596;ka s&#603; &#596;te ne mu no, &#603;s&#603; no s&#603; &#596;nante s&#603;de&#603; &#596;no nso nantee&#603;.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="7">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Ad&#596;fo, &#603;ny&#603; ahy&#603;de&#603; fofor&#596; na meretwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo, na mmom ahy&#603;de&#603; dada a moanya firi mfitiase&#603; no. Ahy&#603;de&#603; dada no ne as&#603;m a moate&#603; no. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="8">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Nso meretwer&#603; ahy&#603;de&#603; fofor&#596; mabr&#603; mo a &#603;y&#603; nokor&#603; w&#596; &#596;no ne mo mu: S&#603; esum retwa mu, na nokor&#603; hann no anya rehyer&#603;n. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="9">
            <block_quote>
                <content> De&#603; &#596;ka s&#603; &#596;w&#596; hann no mu na &#596;tane ne nua no, &#596;da so w&#596; sum mu ara de b&#603;si s&#603;s&#603;&#603;. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="10">
            <block_quote>
                <content>De&#603; &#596;d&#596; ne nua no w&#596; hann no mu, na suntidua nni ne mu. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="11">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na de&#603; &#596;tan ne nua no te sum mu na &#596;nam sum mu, na &#596;nnim de&#603; &#596;rekor&#596;, &#603;firi s&#603; esum no afira n’ani.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="12">
            <block_quote kind="LEFT">
                <content>Mma nkumaa, meretwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo s&#603;,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>ne din nti w&#596;de mo b&#596;ne aky&#603; mo.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="13">
            <block_quote kind="LEFT">
                <content>Agyanom, meretwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>&#603;firi s&#603; monim de&#603; &#596;w&#596; h&#596; firi mfitiase&#603; no.</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT">
                <content>Mmerante&#603;, meretwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo s&#603;,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>moadi &#596;b&#596;nefo&#596; no so nkonim.</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT">
                <content>Mm&#596;fra nkumaa, matwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo s&#603;,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>monim Agya no.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="14">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Agyanom, matwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo s&#603;,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>monim de&#603; &#596;w&#596; h&#596; firi mfitiase&#603; no.</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT">
                <content>Mmerante&#603;, matwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo s&#603;,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>mo ho y&#603; den,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT">
                <content>na Nyankop&#596;n as&#603;m no te mo mu,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na moadi &#596;b&#596;nefo&#596; no so nkonim.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="15">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Monnn&#596; wiase anaa nno&#596;ma a &#603;w&#596; wiase. S&#603; obi d&#596; wiase a, Agya no d&#596; no nni ne mu. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="16">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na de&#603; &#603;w&#596; wiase nyinaa, honam ak&#596;nn&#596; ne aniwa ak&#596;nn&#596; ne asetena mu ahohoahoa, &#603;mfiri Agya no, na mmom &#603;firi wiase. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="17">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na wiase ne n’ak&#596;nn&#596; retwam, na de&#603; &#596;y&#603; ade&#603; a Onyankop&#596;n p&#603; no tena h&#596; daa.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="18">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Mm&#596;fra nkumaa, &#603;d&#596;n a &#603;di akyire nie. Na s&#603;de&#603; moate s&#603; antikristo no reb&#603;ba no, saa na seesei yi antikristo bebree aba; &#603;nna y&#603;de hunu s&#603; d&#596;n a &#603;di akyire nie. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="19">
            <block_quote>
                <content> W&#596;firi y&#603;n mu na &#603;k&#596;e&#603; de&#603;, nanso w&#596;nka y&#603;n ho, na s&#603; w&#596;ka y&#603;n ho a, anka w&#596;ne y&#603;n tenaa h&#596;. Na &#603;y&#603;&#603; saa na w&#596;ada adi s&#603; w&#596;n nyinaa nka y&#603;n ho. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="20">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Na mo de&#603;, moanya ngosra no firi &#390;kronkronni no h&#596;, na mo nyinaa nim de. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="21">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Mantwer&#603; mammr&#603; mo s&#603;de&#603; monnim nokor&#603; no, na mmom s&#603; monim, ne s&#603; ator&#596; biara mfiri nokor&#603; no mu.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="22">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Hwan ne &#596;torofo&#596; no s&#603; de&#603; &#596;sane s&#603; Yesu ny&#603; Kristo no? Oyi ne antikristo a &#596;po Agya no ne &#390;ba no. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="23">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Obiara a &#596;po &#390;ba no, &#596;nni Agya no nso, na de&#603; &#596;pae mu b&#596; &#390;ba no din no, w&#596; Agya no nso. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="24">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Enti mo de&#603;, de&#603; mote firii mfitiase&#603; no, momma no ntena mo mu; na s&#603; de&#603; mote firii mfitiase&#603; no tena mo mu a, &#603;nne&#603; mo nso mob&#603;tena &#390;ba no ne Agya no mu. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="25">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na &#603;b&#596; a &#596;de ahy&#603; y&#603;n ne daa nkwa no.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="26">
            <block_quote>
                <content>De&#603; matwer&#603; mabr&#603; mo yi fa w&#596;n a w&#596;daadaa mo no ho. </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="27">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Na mo de&#603;, ngosra a monyaa no ne nsa mu no te mo mu, enti &#603;nhia mo s&#603; obi kyer&#603;kyer&#603; mo; na mmom s&#603;de&#603; ngosra no ara kyer&#603;kyer&#603; mo ade nyinaa ho no na &#603;y&#603; nokor&#603;, na &#603;ny&#603; ator&#596;. Na s&#603;de&#603; akyer&#603;kyer&#603; mo no, montena ne mu! </content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="28">
            <block_quote>
                <content> Na afei, mma nkumaa, montena ne mu, na s&#603; oyi ne ho adi a, y&#603;anya awer&#603;hy&#603;mu, na y&#603;n ani anwu n’anim, ne ba mu.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="29">
            <block_quote>
                <content> S&#603; monim s&#603; &#596;y&#603; &#596;teneneeni a, anka mob&#603;hunu s&#603; obiara a &#596;y&#603; ade tenenee no, &#596;no na Onyankop&#596;n awo no.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
